EwmhBaseStruts 0 0 0 22

Style "FvwmTaskBar" NoTitle, !Borders, !Handles, Sticky, NeverFocus \
    StaysOnTop, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, FixedPosition, FixedSize, !Iconifiable

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTaskBar: *
*FvwmTaskBar: Geometry +0-0
*FvwmTaskBar: Rows 1
*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click1 DeiconifyRaiseAndFocus
*FvwmTaskBar: Action Click2 Close
*FvwmTaskBar: Font "xft:Sans:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*FvwmTaskBar: SelFont "xft:Sans:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*FvwmTaskBar: StatusFont "xft:Sans:Bold:pixelsize=12:minispace=True:antialias=True"
*FvwmTaskBar: UseSkipList
*FvwmTaskBar: ShowTips
*FvwmTaskBar: StartName FVWM
*FvwmTaskBar: StartCommand (Mouse 1) Popup FvwmRootMenu rectangle $widthx$height+$left+$top 0 -100m
*FvwmTaskBar: StartCommand (Mouse 3) Popup FvwmExitMenu rectangle $widthx$height+$left+$top 0 -100m
*FvwmTaskBar: ClockFormat %l:%M:%S %p
*FvwmTaskBar: UpdateInterval 1

AddToFunc DeiconifyRaiseAndFocus
+ I ThisWindow (Focused) Iconify on
+ I TestRc (NoMatch) Deiconify

AddToFunc Deiconify
+ I Iconify Off
+ I Focus
+ I Raise
